                "text": "L =  + 0 (00)* for given FA. \n\n L0 = {}  \n\n L1 = L0. L = .( + 0(00)*) = L \n\n L2 = L1. L = L.L  = [ + 0(00)*] [ + 0(00)*]  = 0* \n\n L3 = L2. L =  0*. ( + 0 (00)*)  = 0* \n\nSo, O(L) = 2",
