            "question": {
                "text": "Language L1 is defined by the grammar:   \nS1 \\rightarrow aS1b |  \n\nLanguage L2 is defined by the grammar: \nS2 \\rightarrow abS2 |   \n\nConsider the following statements: \n\nP: L1 is regular \n\nQ: L2 is regular \n\nWhich of the following is TRUE?",
