            "solution": {
                "text": "• \nS1 \\rightarrow aS1b |  \nL1 = {an bn | n \\ge 0} is CFL \n• \nS2 \\rightarrow abS2 |  \nL2 = (ab)* is Regular \n\nHence, L1 is CFL and L2 is Regular. \n\nSo, option (c) is correct.",
